### 查询房源列表
GET http://localhost:8000/api/houses?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1. 创建租住订单
POST http://localhost:8000/api/rent-orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "houseId": "house-1",
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "leaseMonths": 12,
  "paymentMethod": "monthly",
  "tenantCount": 1
}


### 2. 查询订单详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 3. 提交实名认证
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/real-name
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "tenantName": "张小杰",
  "tenantPhone": "13213592847",
  "tenantIdCard": "500212200001011234"
}


### 4. 获取合同预览
### 获取合同预览
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/contract-preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 确认合同
POST http://localhost:8000/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/confirm-contract
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 获取支付信息
GET http://localhost:8000/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/payment-info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 模拟支付
POST http://localhost:8000/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/pay
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "paymentMethod": "wechat"
}


### 8. 在线签约
POST http://localhost:8000/api/rent-orders/{{orderId}}/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### 9. 查询我的租约
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leases/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}